WEBVTT

00:06:29.114 --> 00:06:33.208
(Laughter)

00:06:33.738 --> 00:06:38.801
"You call them boogers.
Greg calls them delicious little sugars."

00:06:38.825 --> 00:06:40.118
(Laughter)

00:06:40.142 --> 00:06:44.086
That laugh, that positive reaction

00:06:44.110 --> 00:06:46.541
or gross reaction some of you just had,

00:06:46.565 --> 00:06:47.732
(Laughter)

00:06:47.756 --> 00:06:51.775
black boys deserve
and desperately need more of that.

00:06:53.082 --> 00:06:57.496
Dismantling the savage inequalities
that plague American education

00:06:57.520 --> 00:07:01.150
requires us to create reading experiences